(9, 6, '1667796717_One Bedroom.webp', 'One Bedroom Pool Villa', 2, 1, 'Pool View', 'King Bed or Twin Beds', 280, 'Private pool,\r\nPrivate cabana,\r\nGourmet bar,\r\nOutdoor dining area,\r\n24-hour butler service,\r\n43” flat-screen TV,\r\nIndividual climate control,\r\nBlackout curtains,\r\nHair dryer,\r\nBranded bath amenities,\r\nPlush robes and slippers,\r\nCoffee maker,\r\nMinifridge,\r\nIron and ironing board on request,\r\nIn-room safe,\r\nDaily newspaper on request,\r\nRollaway bed on request,', '私人泳池，\r\n私人小屋，\r\n美食酒吧，\r\n戶外用餐區，\r\n24小時管家服務，\r\n43吋平面電視，\r\n獨立溫控，\r\n遮光窗簾，\r\n吹風機，\r\n品牌盥洗用品，\r\n豪華浴袍和拖鞋，\r\n咖啡機，\r\n迷你冰箱，\r\n熨斗和熨衣板（可應要求提供），\r\n客房內保險箱，\r\n每日報紙（可應要求提供），\r\n折疊床（可應要求提供），', '私人泳池，\r\n私人小屋，\r\n美食酒吧，\r\n户外用餐区，\r\n24小时管家服务，\r\n43英寸平板电视，\r\n独立温控，\r\n遮光窗帘，\r\n吹风机，\r\n品牌洗浴用品，\r\n豪华浴袍和拖鞋，\r\n咖啡机，\r\n迷你冰箱，\r\n熨斗和熨衣板（可应要求提供），\r\n客房内保险箱，\r\n每日报纸（可应要求提供），\r\n折叠床（可应要求提供）', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily a la carte breakfast</li><li>Host (butler) service</li><li>Wi-Fi Internet access throughout the resort</li><li>Morning yoga session from 07.30 - 08.30 am</li><li>Use of 24-hour Gym</li><li>24-hour Library</li><li>Alila Living bath amenities</li><li>Complimentary drop off and pick up service to and from Savaya</li></ul>', NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-05 17:51:57', '2025-10-07 08:10:22'),
(11, 6, '1667800629_three Bedroom Hillside villa.webp', 'Three Bedroom Hillside Villa', 6, 3, 'Ocean View', 'King Bed', 3000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily a la carte breakfast</li><li>Host (butler) service</li><li>Wi-Fi Internet access throughout the resort</li><li>Morning yoga session from 07.30 - 08.30 am</li><li>Use of 24-hour Gym</li><li>24-hour Library</li><li>Alila Living bath amenities</li><li>Complimentary drop off and pick up service to and from Savaya</li></ul>', NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-05 18:57:09', '2026-01-09 03:46:16'),
(12, 6, '1667800677_3 BR Cliffedge Villa.webp', 'Three Bedroom Cliff Edge Villa', 6, 3, 'Ocean View', 'King Bed', 3000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Daily a la carte breakfast</li><li>Host (butler) service</li><li>Wi-Fi Internet access throughout the resort</li><li>Morning yoga session from 07.30 - 08.30 am</li><li>Use of 24-hour Gym</li><li>24-hour Library</li><li>Alila Living bath amenities</li><li>Complimentary drop off and pick up service to and from Savaya</li></ul>', NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-05 18:57:57', '2026-01-09 03:52:02'),
(13, 11, '1759977173_One Badroom Garden Pool Villa.jpg', '1BR Tropical Garden Pool Villa', 2, 1, 'Garden view, Pool view', 'King Bed', 403, '<ul><li>400 thread count sheets</li><li>65-inch HDTV</li><li>Air conditioning</li><li>Bath slippers</li><li>Bathrobe</li><li>Bidet</li><li>Black-Out Curtains</li><li>Chaise lounge</li><li>Clock Radio W/CD Player</li><li>Complimentary Pillow Menu</li><li>Dining table</li><li>Down Pillows Available</li><li>Duvet Covers</li><li>Easy to Set Alarm Clock Radio</li><li>Feather Pillows Non Allergenic</li><li>HD Channels</li><li>Jetted tub</li><li>Lever Door Handles</li><li>Night Lights in Bathroom</li><li>Non-Smoking</li><li>Radio alarm clock</li><li>Seating area with sofa</li><li>Separate bathtub and shower</li><li>Separate toilet area</li><li>Sleeps 3</li><li>Thermostat (adjustable)</li><li>TV - 55 Inch Flat Panel HD</li><li>TV-Cable</li><li>TV-Standard Network</li><li>Workstation</li></ul>', '<ul><li>400 支紗床單、&nbsp;</li><li>65 吋高清電視、&nbsp;</li><li>空調、</li><li>浴室拖鞋、</li><li>浴袍、</li><li>坐浴盆、</li><li>遮光窗簾、</li><li>躺椅、&nbsp;</li><li>附 CD 播放器的時鐘收音機、&nbsp;</li><li>免費、</li><li>枕頭選單、&nbsp;</li><li>餐桌、&nbsp;</li><li>羽絨枕（可選）、&nbsp;</li><li>羽絨被套、&nbsp;</li><li>易於設定的鬧鐘收音機、&nbsp;</li><li>防過敏羽絨枕頭、&nbsp;</li><li>高清頻道、&nbsp;</li><li>按摩浴缸、&nbsp;</li><li>槓桿門把手、&nbsp;</li><li>浴室夜燈、&nbsp;</li><li>禁煙\r\n收音機鬧鐘、&nbsp;</li><li>附沙發的休息區、&nbsp;</li><li>獨立浴缸和淋浴間、&nbsp;</li><li>獨立衛浴、&nbsp;</li><li>可容納 3 人、&nbsp;</li><li>恆溫器（可調節）、&nbsp;</li><li>55 吋高清平面電視、&nbsp;</li><li>有線電視、&nbsp;</li><li>標準電視、</li><li>網路、&nbsp;</li><li>工作站</li></ul>', '<ul><li>400 支纱床单、&nbsp;</li><li>65 英寸高清电视、&nbsp;</li><li>空调、&nbsp;</li><li>浴室拖鞋、&nbsp;</li><li>浴袍、&nbsp;</li><li>坐浴盆、&nbsp;</li><li>遮光窗帘、&nbsp;</li><li>躺椅、&nbsp;</li><li>带 CD 播放器的时钟收音机、</li><li>&nbsp;免费、</li><li>枕头选单、</li><li>&nbsp;餐桌、&nbsp;</li><li>羽绒枕（可选）、&nbsp;</li><li>羽绒被套、&nbsp;</li><li>易于设置的闹钟收音机、&nbsp;</li><li>防过敏羽绒枕头、&nbsp;</li><li>高清频道、&nbsp;</li><li>按摩浴缸、&nbsp;</li><li>杠杆门把手、&nbsp;</li><li>浴室夜灯、&nbsp;</li><li>禁烟\r\n收音机闹钟、&nbsp;</li><li>带沙发的休息区、&nbsp;</li><li>独立浴缸和淋浴间、</li><li>&nbsp;独立卫生间、&nbsp;</li><li>可容纳 3 人、&nbsp;</li><li>恒温器（可调节）、&nbsp;</li><li>55 英寸高清平板电视、&nbsp;</li><li>有线电视、&nbsp;</li><li>标准电视、</li><li>网络、&nbsp;</li><li>工作站</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Welcome drink upon arrival&nbsp;</li><li>Welcome amenities upon arrival in the villa for special occasion \r\n(birthday/anniversary/honeymooner/VIP) must be inform upon make a \r\nbooking&nbsp;</li><li>Birthday amenities : birthday cake&nbsp;</li><li>Honeymoon : red yukata, red rose and swan art towel on the bathtub&nbsp;</li><li>Anniversary : red rose &amp; swan art towel on the bed&nbsp;</li><li>Bathroom amenities&nbsp;</li><li>Curator Service 24/7&nbsp;</li><li>6 bottles of mineral water per day, in-room coffee &amp; tea making facilities (1BR \r\nPool Villa)&nbsp;</li><li>10 bottles of mineral water per day, in-room coffee &amp; tea making facilities (2BR \r\nPool Villa)&nbsp;</li><li>24 bottles of mineral water per day, in-room coffee &amp; tea making facilities (3BR \r\nPool Villa)&nbsp;</li><li>Daily breakfast Commune Restaurant&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi at resorts area&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary access to Kids Club&nbsp;</li><li>Daily turndown Service with different souvenir</li><li>Complimentary shuttle service to Melasti Beach / UMA Beach house&nbsp;</li><li>Daily free yoga session at 07:30 A.M, in yoga pavilion</li></ul>', NULL, 'Active', '2022-11-05 19:47:03', '2025-10-09 02:32:53'),
(14, 11, '1759977143_One Bedroom Ocen View Villa.jpg', '1BR Partial Ocean Pool Villa', 2, 1, 'Ocean View', 'King Bed', 403, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Welcome drink upon arrival&nbsp;</li><li>Welcome amenities upon arrival in the villa for special occasion (birthday/anniversary/honeymooner/VIP) must be inform upon make a booking&nbsp;</li><li>Birthday amenities : birthday cake&nbsp;</li><li>Honeymoon : red yukata, red rose and swan art towel on the bathtub&nbsp;</li><li>Anniversary : red rose &amp; swan art towel on the bed&nbsp;</li><li>Bathroom amenities&nbsp;</li><li>Curator Service 24/7&nbsp;</li><li>6 bottles of mineral water per day, in-room coffee &amp; tea making facilities (1BR Pool Villa)&nbsp;</li><li>10 bottles of mineral water per day, in-room coffee &amp; tea making facilities (2BR Pool Villa)&nbsp;</li><li>24 bottles of mineral water per day, in-room coffee &amp; tea making facilities (3BR Pool Villa)&nbsp;</li><li>Daily breakfast Commune Restaurant&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi at resorts area&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary access to Kids Club&nbsp;</li><li>Daily turndown Service with different souvenir</li><li>Complimentary shuttle service to Melasti Beach / UMA Beach house&nbsp;</li><li>Daily free yoga session at 07:30 A.M, in yoga pavilion</li></ul>', '<br>', 'Active', '2022-11-05 19:49:20', '2025-10-09 02:32:23'),
