(31, 21, '1668405501_garden club chalet- Padma Legian.webp', 'Garden Club Chalet', 2, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Club Lounge check in service</li><li>In-room welcome flower and special fruit basket upon arrival</li><li>1 (one) time Laundry service per stay for max. 5 pieces (excluding dry cleaning)</li><li>1 (one) time complimentary minibar set up upon arrival&nbsp;</li><li>Breakfast venue options at Club Lounge or DONBIU</li><li>Daily refreshment at Club Lounge from 11 AM - 11 PM&nbsp;</li><li>Evening Cocktails*, at Club Lounge is available from 5 PM&nbsp;&ndash; 7 PM</li><li>10% off on food at Themed Buffet Dinner**</li></ul>', '<ul><li>During Evening Cocktails Hours, children below the age of 13 years old are not to be in or around the Lounge.&nbsp;</li><li>Children can enjoy supervised playtime and complimentary refreshments at Kids Club &amp; Games Centre.&nbsp;</li><li>Alcohol beverages will not be served for guest under 18 years old.&nbsp;</li><li>Cannot be combined with any other promotions and only valid if themed dinner is available in the resort&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'Draft', '2022-11-12 18:58:21', '2025-04-02 01:02:59'),
