(56, 26, '1732009089_The sebali.webp', '1BR Pool Villa with Valley View', 2, 1, 'Valley View', 'King Bed', 56, NULL, NULL, NULL, '家庭套餐：\r\n每間客房最多可入住兩人。\r\n鑑於飯店的設計，我們強烈建議您不要攜帶15歲以下的兒童入住。\r\n如果客人堅持攜帶15歲以下的兒童入住，請在入住時簽署《兒童免責聲明協議書》。\r\n最多可攜帶1名兒童免費入住，但需與父母共用現有床位。否則，我們建議您加床或額外增加房間。', '家庭套餐：\r\n每间客房最多可入住两人。\r\n鉴于酒店的设计，我们强烈建议您不要携带15岁以下的儿童入住。\r\n如果客人坚持携带15岁以下的儿童入住，请在入住时签署《儿童免责声明协议书》。\r\n最多可携带1名儿童免费入住，但需与父母共用现有床位。否则，我们建议您加床或额外增加房间。', '<ul><li>Welcome Drink and cool towel upon arrival</li><li>Daily choice of ala carte Breakfast</li><li>Complimentary daily Replenish mineral water in the room</li><li>Free daily afternoon tea</li><li>Free daily seasonal fruit basket in room</li><li>Free Shuttle to Ubud Center Based on Schedule</li><li>Free daily refill mini bar (all item)</li></ul>', 'Family Plan:<ul><li>The maximum number of occupants per room is two persons</li><li>Considering the design of the property, we are strongly not recommending for the kids under 15 years old to stay at our property.</li><li>In the case that the guest insists to bring their Kids under 15 years old, guest should sign the Children Disclaimer Agreement Letter upon check in.</li><li>Maximum1 kid may stay free of charge by sharing existing bed with parents, otherwise we encourage to add extra bed or extra room.</li></ul>', 'Active', '2022-11-15 17:55:18', '2025-10-09 04:08:00'),
(57, 26, '1732009238_river view.webp', '1BR Pool Villa with River View', 2, 1, 'River View', 'Queen bed', 56, NULL, NULL, NULL, '家庭套餐：\r\n每間客房最多可入住兩人。\r\n鑑於飯店的設計，我們強烈建議您不要攜帶15歲以下的兒童入住。\r\n如果客人堅持攜帶15歲以下的兒童入住，請在入住時簽署《兒童免責聲明協議書》。\r\n最多可攜帶1名兒童免費入住，但需與父母共用現有床位。否則，我們建議您加床或額外增加房間。', '家庭套餐：\r\n每间客房最多可入住两人。\r\n鉴于酒店的设计，我们强烈建议您不要携带15岁以下的儿童入住。\r\n如果客人坚持携带15岁以下的儿童入住，请在入住时签署《儿童免责声明协议书》。\r\n最多可携带1名儿童免费入住，但需与父母共用现有床位。否则，我们建议您加床或额外增加房间。', '<ul><li>Welcome Drink and cool towel upon arrival</li><li>Daily choice of ala carte Breakfast</li><li>Complimentary daily Replenish mineral water in the room</li><li>Free daily afternoon tea</li><li>Free daily seasonal fruit basket in room</li><li>Free Shuttle to Ubud Center Based on Schedule</li><li>Free daily refill mini bar (all item)</li></ul>', 'Family Plan:<ul><li>The maximum number of occupants per room is two persons</li><li>Considering the design of the property, we are strongly not recommending for the kids under 15 years old to stay at our property.</li><li>In the case that the guest insists to bring their Kids under 15 years old, guest should sign the Children Disclaimer Agreement Letter upon check in.</li><li>Maximum1 kid may stay free of charge by sharing existing bed with parents, otherwise we encourage to add extra bed or extra room.</li></ul>', 'Active', '2022-11-15 17:56:52', '2025-10-09 04:10:39'),
