(238, 56, '1669623471_Jungle Suite.webp', 'Jungle Suite', 2, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<b>Breakfast inclusive rates conditions:</b><ul><li>In-house pouring water, coffee and tea, juice of the day at breakfast.</li><li>All the above rates are for single (1) or double (2) occupancy for a Suite or One-Bedroom Villa or four (4) occupants for a Two-Bedroom Villa. Supplement charges apply for extra person.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>Breakfast is only available at our All Day Dining restaurant – KEPUH.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ul><b>SUITE &amp; VILLA RATES STANDARD INCLUSIONS:&nbsp;</b><ul><li>Complimentary daily Kappa Senses’ instant as per resort’s schedule.</li><li>Complimentary shuttle service to a designated area in Ubud town based on the resort’s schedule.</li><li>Complimentary Wi-Fi in rooms and throughout the resort.</li><li>Complimentary use of the gym and two resort’s swimming pool.</li><li>Complimentary welcome drink.</li><li>Complimentary local bottled water – replenished daily.</li><li>Complimentary fruit basket – replenished daily.</li><li>Complimentary in-room coffee and tea making facilities.</li><li>Complimentary access to smart TV services (40 International Chain HD TV Channels, HBO Go, Netflix).&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'Size: 77 sqm / 829 ft²&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;', 'Active', '2022-11-26 21:17:51', '2025-05-14 03:40:02'),
